attributes.imdb: http://www.imdb.com/name/nm2162079/'''Ivailo Dimitrov''' is a stunt performer from Bulgaria. He worked as Jason Momoa's stunt double on ''Conan'' before joining the team for ''Game of Thrones''. He played Dothraki rider Mago.==See also==*Template:IMDb
